            <p class="overview-card-desc">Gennemse og eksportér den aktuelle fadølsliste til skiltning og menukort.</p>
            <span class="overview-card-link">Se fadølsliste <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
        </a>

        <a class="overview-card" href="kategorier">
            <span class="overview-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M9.568 3H5.25A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 3 5.25v4.318c0 .597.237 1.17.659 1.591l9.581 9.581c.699.699 1.78.872 2.607.33a18.095 18.095 0 0 0 5.223-5.223c.542-.827.369-1.908-.33-2.607L11.16 3.66A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 9.568 3Z" />
                    <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M6 6h.008v.008H6V6Z" />
                </svg>
            </span>
            <h2 class="overview-card-title">Kategorier</h2>
            <p class="overview-card-desc">Administrér produktkategorier, prismærker og ekstra kolonner for prislisten.</p>
            <span class="overview-card-link">Administrér kategorier <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
        </a>

        <a class="overview-card" href="produkter">
            <span class="overview-card-icon" aria-hidden="true">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke-width="1.5" stroke="currentColor">
