                    <polyline stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" points="3.27 6.96 12 12.01 20.73 6.96" />
                    <line stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" x1="12" y1="22.08" x2="12" y2="12" />
                </svg>
            </span>
            <h2 class="overview-card-title">Produkter</h2>
            <p class="overview-card-desc">Gennemse, filtrér og rediger produktkataloget — inkl. priser, størrelser og manglende felter.</p>
            <span class="overview-card-link">Administrér produkter <span aria-hidden="true">→</span></span>
        </a>
